1. On *glumi* u pozorištu već pet godina. (She acts in the theater for five years already.) 
2. Ja sam *glumio* u školskoj predstavi. (I acted in a school play.) 
3. Da li si ti nekada *glumio* u životu? (Have you ever acted in your life?) 
4. Oni *glume* u filmu koji se snima ovde. (They are acting in a movie that is being filmed here.) 
5. On *glumi* da zna sve, ali zapravo nema pojma. (He pretends to know everything, but actually he has no clue.) 
6. Ona *glumi* da je srećna, ali vidim da nije. (She pretends to be happy, but I can see she's not.) 
7. Glumac koji *glumi* u ovom filmu dobio je nagradu za najbolju mušku ulogu. (The actor who plays in this movie received an award for the best male role.) 
8. Nemoj mi *glumiti* žrtvu, znam da si ti kriv! (Don't pretend to be a victim, I know you are guilty!)